channel.title: [317] ::players command
channel.description: Simple question, simple answer. I edited my ::yell command and accidentally removed half of my ::players command. now when you type ::players it just sends a message saying how many people are online, instead of the quest pop up showing whos online and where. can anyone get me the command?

item.description:

Just rip it from the base you used?
